description:

name: Keyboard Name Necklace/Pin! *Any Word you want!*
description:
Calling all indie kids!

Roll up for your very own individual custom made keyboard necklace or badge!

This is the ultimate accessorie for any fashion loving eco-warrior. Made form old Computer keys and attached to either a silver plated chain or metal badge attchment - it's the definition of trashy chic.

As they are handmade by billy @ I_Arr_Pirate, you can choose from any key on the board from letters, numbers, escape keys, space bars, whatever you want - mix it up and make it your own!

A truely unique item for freaky girls & boys.

Currently only 4 in exsistance so buy 1 now and become a member of I_Arrr_Pirate's exclusive club!

PLEASE TELL ME THE LETTERS YOU WANT IN THE CHECKOUT!

NB: Maxium amount of keys on 1 necklace or badge is 6 (for more please contact me for price information). Some keys may be slightly different( like the L's in billy) but this just adds to the quirky charm.
Please allow up to 2 weeks before reciving your product to allow for making time.

For more pictures or if you have ANY questions about my products, feel free to ask.
